---
// ServicesPreview.astro
// Beranda - Layanan Utama (ringkas)
// Three cards: Simpanan, Pinjaman, Pendekatan - no rates, no calculators
---

<section class="bg-neutral-50 py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="container-content">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between gap-6 mb-12"
    >
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-primary mb-4"
        >
          Layanan
        </p>
        <h2
          class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 leading-snug"
        >
          Layanan yang bekerja<br class="hidden md:block" /> untuk anggota
        </h2>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/layanan"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary hover:text-primary/80 font-medium text-sm transition-colors shrink-0"
      >
        Lihat penjelasan lengkap
        <svg
          class="w-4 h-4"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Simpanan -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 border border-neutral-100 flex flex-col"
      >
        <div
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-primary"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.8"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0 1 15.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 0 0 3 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5Zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">
          Simpanan Anggota
        </h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">
          Simpanan adalah fondasi keikutsertaan Anda di KSP CUSS. Setiap rupiah
          yang ditabung memperkuat modal bersama dan meningkatkan akses layanan
          Anda ke depannya. Tersedia berbagai jenis simpanan sesuai tujuan dan
          kebutuhan.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pinjaman -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 border border-neutral-100 flex flex-col"
      >
        <div
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-primary"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.8"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M12 3v17.25m0 0c-1.472 0-2.882.265-4.185.75M12 20.25c1.472 0 2.882.265 4.185.75M18.75 4.97A48.416 48.416 0 0 0 12 4.5c-2.291 0-4.545.16-6.75.47m13.5 0c1.01.143 2.01.317 3 .52m-3-.52 2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.988 5.988 0 0 1-2.031.352 5.988 5.988 0 0 1-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L18.75 4.97Zm-16.5.52c.99-.203 1.99-.377 3-.52m0 0 2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.989 5.989 0 0 1-2.031.352 5.989 5.989 0 0 1-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L5.25 4.97Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">
          Pinjaman Bertanggung Jawab
        </h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">
          Pinjaman di KSP CUSS adalah bentuk gotong royong, bukan produk
          komersial. Setiap permohonan dinilai secara cermat oleh Panitia Kredit
          berdasarkan kebutuhan nyata dan kemampuan mengembalikan, bukan
          semata-mata jumlah agunan.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pendekatan Layanan -->
      <div
        class="bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col"
      >
        <div
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white/15 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-foreground"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.8"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl text-primary-foreground font-semibold mb-3">
          Pendekatan Berbeda
        </h3>
        <p class="text-primary-foreground/80 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-1">
          Sisa Hasil Usaha dikembalikan kepada anggota, bukan kepada pemegang
          saham luar. Semakin aktif Anda menabung dan meminjam, semakin besar
          manfaat yang Anda terima setiap akhir tahun buku.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/layanan"
          class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-foreground font-medium text-sm hover:gap-3 transition-all"
        >
          Pelajari selengkapnya
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
